trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal"></xref> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal"> </xref> Web serverkontroll.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control allows a text string to be used as a control on a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontrollen kan en tekststreng som skal brukes som en kontroll på en webside.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter fra kilden til utformingsvisning markup kildekode som beskriver en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontrollen analyseres og en utformingen versjon av kontrollen er opprettet på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to the markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du går tilbake til visning i datakilden, er utformingen kontrollen beholdt i markup kildekode og redigeres i markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: The LiteralDesigner class provides design-time support for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen LiteralDesigner gir støtte for utforming for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LiteralDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A> method is called when there is a design-time change to the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LiteralDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A>metoden ved utformingen, endres den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LiteralDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LiteralDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LiteralDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LiteralDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control or a copy of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LiteralDesigner>klasse når det oppretter den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontroll eller en kopi av det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontrollen i utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LiteralDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Called when there is a change to the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Kalles når det er en endring i den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The OnComponentChanged method is called when the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged> event of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control is raised.
trans-unit.target: Metoden OnComponentChanged kalles når den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>hendelse for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontrollen aktiveres.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>

trans-unit.source: Typically, this is in response to a property change on the control (for example, a `Properties` grid change).
trans-unit.target: Dette er vanligvis som svar på en endring av kontrollen (for eksempel en `Properties` rutenett endre).

trans-unit.source: The OnComponentChanged creates a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs> object and then calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A> base method.
trans-unit.target: OnComponentChanged oppretter en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs>objekt og kall av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A>basere metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The object that is the source of the event.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som er kilde for hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs"></xref> object that contains the event data.
